From this balance sheet, however, 5 Gt would still have to be subtracted to stabilise the climate increase by 2 degrees Celsius from today until 2020, in order to prevent it from being out of control.
In the white glowing pears 95% of the energy escapes in the form of heat, and the remaining 5% produce the light.
The compact light bulbs reduce energy consumption by 75%, while the new LED light bulbs reduce this energy demand by twice as much.
